name: STAYwise Tank Tops
description:
Our tank tops are extremely basic in design. They contain organic cotton blend material, and are made to be worn during the hottest days. Our STAYwise tank tops features our GothiKa design. 

Each product is given a Product Number (PN). Our A class products is our products for Women, and our B class products is our products for Men. Products that are unisex (for BOTH men and women) will be designated as such.
